data.title: Delaware Prosperity Partnership
data.meta_description: Learn about Delaware's major industries, including financial services, chemicals, advanced materials and manufacturing, and more.
data.meta_site_name: Business in Delaware | Delaware Prosperity Partnership
data.text:
With the second-lowest business costs in the United States, Delaware is home to a diverse range of industries that support businesses large and small. Together with our world-class research universities, internationally-oriented workforce and competitive cost of doing business, Delaware is positioned perfectly to welcome new business and capital investment.

Want to know more about Delawareâ€™s major industries? From our dominant legacy in chemicals to pioneering leadership of the financial services industry, read on to learn why global companies like DuPont, Bank of America, Capital One and more do business in Delaware.
